  <prompt>
    Implement the regarding field population logic in AssociationResolver. When a user selects
    a record, the control must: (1) set the appropriate entity-specific lookup field, (2) set
    the denormalized reference fields (name, type), (3) clear other lookup fields.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    SPAARKE platform developer with expertise in PCF control development and Dataverse form APIs.
    Understand the dual-field strategy for polymorphic lookups.
  </role>

  <goal>
    When a record is selected in AssociationResolver, the correct lookup field is populated,
    denormalized fields are set, and other lookups are cleared. Form state is properly updated.
  </goal>

  <context>
